   "source": [
    "Traditional Computing \n",
    "The loss is defined as $L = (y - \\hat{y})^2$\n",
    "$$\n",
    "L = \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n}(y_i - \\hat{y}_i)^2\n",
    "$$"
   ]
